result.execSummary:
The defendant Melissa M Christensen was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Melissa M Christensen is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Melissa M Christensen was found guilty of Possession of THC (2nd+ Offense), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
